de.stroeer.proxity.gateway

Interface Gateway.IGatewayListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnalyticsService, BackgroundService, OutdoorPositioningManager
    Enclosing class:
    Gateway

    public static interface Gateway.IGatewayListener
    This class is the inforamtion interface between app and sdk. Every change in status and event which occures inside of the sdk will be notified on this Listener. The different types of information are separated in three classes. Each time a specific status was gained (for example: Bluetooth enabled, Internet connection available) will be notified via onStatusGained(StroeerProxityApi, SdkStatus, boolean) . Each time a status is revoked, the onStatusRevoked(StroeerProxityApi, SdkStatus, boolean) will be called. If there is any message(for example: Created new User, download of data finished) or new data(for example: new location) which should be sent to the app the onMessage(StroeerProxityApi, Message, boolean) will be called.
